Copy and Report On Search Results

With the new Copy Records and Create Report search actions, your users can now save and share search result details by copying data or creating a report directly from search results.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience editions where Criteria-Based Search and Filter is enabled.

Who: Users with the Criteria-Based Search and Filter system permission can configure and use criteria-based search and filter capabilities.

How: To use the Copy Records action, create a search action that specifies the Copy Records Lightning web component. To use the Create Report action, save the Create Report flow as a new flow...
title: Copy and Share Search Results in Salesforce
